      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d230n1-ptr" id="PJA06d230n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Not found, nor is it known whether it dealt with the effort, described by Coffyn, to outfit a privateer at Dunkirk. For the background of that affair see Peter Amiel, Oath of Allegiance, 23 June, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0173&amp;expandNote=PJA06d200n1#PJA06d200n1" class="document">note 1</a> and references there (above).</p>

